abstract: Coverage and analysis of the Jets' game against the Dolphins on "Monday Night Football."
snippet: Coverage and analysis of the Jets' game against the Dolphins on "Monday Night Football."
lead_paragraph: So is this officially the Jets' first must-win game of the season? Coach Rex Ryan thinks so, and not just because the Jets need to get back to .500 after losing three in a row on the road at Oakland, Baltimore and New England.

headline.main: Tracking Jets vs. Dolphins on 'Monday Night Football'
